title: ROBOTECH - The Complete Comic Pack (1984-2008)
description:
The Complete Robotech Comic Collection, UnRARed and all separate files. This is actually the original source of that other RARed torrent(Notice the similar file size). Don't know why nobody got around to sharing this after so many years but here.

Included folders & files:

1.DC Comics (1984)
2.Comico Comics (1984-1989)
3.Blackthorne Publishing (1987-1988)
4.Eternity/Malibu Comics (1988-1994)
5.Academy Comics (1994-1996)
6.Antarctic Press (1997-1998)
7.DC/Wildstorm Comics (2002-2009)
8.Extras: Robotech Cards, Robotech Comics Reading Order, The Donning Company (1986-1988) - Robotech Art

I couldn't check every file, but comments were good where I got this. I'll be giving it a decent seed to start it off, but I can't support it forever. Please seed as much as you can.
